WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:02.710
All right, let's get started.

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:05.590
Good morning, evening, or wherever you

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:08.230
are. Good morning, family. It's almost

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:10.950
morning. We're going to go over some

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:14.950
things that we saw yesterday in prayer,

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:16.550
and we just want to give God all the

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:18.630
glory for what he does on this channel.

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:20.790
I told Diana while we

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.150
were talking today that we

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:25.910
have one of the largest prayer gatherings in the

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:29.109
world as far as

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:31.029
coming on and praying and having a

00:00:31.039 --> 00:00:33.350
channel for prayer. We have one of the

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:36.870
largest, if not the largest, prayer

00:00:36.880 --> 00:00:39.990
channels in the world, and

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.950
that is consistent.

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:44.630
People pray all the time, but isn't

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:47.110
Jesus wonderful for what he has done on

00:00:47.120 --> 00:00:49.190
here? I just give all the glory to

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:51.029
Jesus. I said, 'Lord, that we would make

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:54.150
your name great.'Father,

00:00:54.150 --> 00:00:54.160
I am

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:56.389
just telling

00:00:56.399 --> 00:00:58.869
the people that

00:00:58.879 --> 00:01:02.389
you're coming. It is exciting to see what

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:04.710
you're doing on this channel. But I want

00:01:04.720 --> 00:01:08.630
to go over some things.

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:12.070
Braden, isn't it amazing that we had

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:14.390
Atlanta today on the news concerning the

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:17.109
airport?

00:01:17.119 --> 00:01:19.590
Baby, could you read that?

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:32.469
'Terror

00:01:32.479 --> 00:01:34.950
aboard Frontier flight as loaded gun

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:37.429
magazine is found near seat as it

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:42.310
prepared to depart Atlanta

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:44.950
airport.'I

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:47.749
said the Atlanta airport is

00:01:47.759 --> 00:01:50.389
highlighted to me now. Is that what I

00:01:50.399 --> 00:01:52.149
was shown?

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:53.270
No.

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:57.590
Is this a coincidence?

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:01.190
No. God works in

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:03.510
mysterious ways, they always say. But

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:06.789
what if that one incident of us praying

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:10.949
even last night causes them to

00:02:10.949 --> 00:02:10.959
get—I

00:02:10.959 --> 00:02:12.949
don't want to say fired, as

00:02:12.949 --> 00:02:12.959
someone

00:02:12.959 --> 00:02:14.470
might have lost their job over that—but

00:02:14.470 --> 00:02:14.480
it

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:18.949
got enough attention

00:02:18.959 --> 00:02:22.630
from the media to

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:24.710
say, 'Listen, you all need to be paying

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:27.589
attention even more so during this

00:02:27.589 --> 00:02:27.599
Thanksgiving.'It

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:30.070
only takes a

00:02:30.070 --> 00:02:30.080
few

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:32.949
people because people can become

00:02:32.949 --> 00:02:32.959
laxadaisical

00:02:32.959 --> 00:02:36.949
in their job after

00:02:36.959 --> 00:02:39.990
doing something for so long. All it

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.229
takes is a little bit

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:45.509
to get their attention.

00:02:45.519 --> 00:02:48.390
What if this was the attention

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:51.830
that was needed for them

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:54.070
to start doing their job more

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:55.030
effectively

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:58.630
to catch what we're praying about

00:02:58.630 --> 00:02:58.640
regarding

00:02:58.640 --> 00:03:01.110
Atlanta? I said, 'Lord, that

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:03.030
coincidence.'It

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:06.470
wasn't Miami; it wasn't New York; it

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:09.270
was Atlanta. Diana and the

00:03:09.270 --> 00:03:09.280
staff were

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:10.390
like, 'We've got to go over

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:12.470
things; we've

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.229
got to talk about

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:16.869
this. We don't know how we missed this.

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:19.509
This is a big mishap, a gun ammo clip,

00:03:19.519 --> 00:03:21.670
and all this stuff. We have

00:03:21.670 --> 00:03:21.680
to

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:24.149
make

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:26.710
sure security is

00:03:26.710 --> 00:03:26.720
tighter.'And

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:31.190
I thought, 'Isn't Jesus

00:03:31.190 --> 00:03:31.200
wonderful?'I

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:33.830
know that he works,

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:36.949
and I see his hand in this. No

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:38.949
one was hurt

00:03:38.949 --> 00:03:38.959
or

00:03:38.959 --> 00:03:41.750
injured.

00:03:41.760 --> 00:03:44.309
A gun clip is harmless without the

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:46.149
firearm,

00:03:46.159 --> 00:03:49.509
but it's enough to raise awareness

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:52.149
to make them super

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:55.670
attentive to their jobs for this

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:58.949
Thanksgiving holiday season because

00:03:58.959 --> 00:04:01.830
those employees, I guarantee you, will

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:03.750
be thinking, 'I don't want to get in trouble

00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:05.990
or fired

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.910
if we let something like this

00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:09.750
happen

00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:09.760
again.'I

00:04:09.760 --> 00:04:11.750
thought,

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:14.149
'Wow, Diana, that

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:16.469
cannot be a

00:04:16.469 --> 00:04:16.479
coincidence.'So

00:04:16.479 --> 00:04:20.229
I just give all the glory to God

00:04:20.239 --> 00:04:23.909
for that.

00:04:23.919 --> 00:04:25.350
One of the

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:27.510
major city airports the Lord

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:29.670
highlighted to me was Atlanta. He said, 'Pray over

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:33.189
Atlanta. This is a

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:34.950
hot

00:04:34.950 --> 00:04:34.960
spot.'And

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:36.469
when it happened today, people were

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:38.070
saying, 'Braden, is this the hot spot?

00:04:38.080 --> 00:04:39.830
Is this what you saw?'I'm like,

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:43.189
'No, it's much worse. What

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:45.909
the Lord showed me was a catastrophic

00:04:45.919 --> 00:04:47.670
event.'But

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:52.710
God, prayer changes things.

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:56.790
I believe this is a result of prayer

00:04:56.800 --> 00:05:00.070
working on our behalf already.

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:06.950
Don't put God in a box. You might

00:05:06.950 --> 00:05:06.960
think they're

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:09.110
going to apprehend a guy

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:11.590
with a carry-on bag

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:13.189
and a SWAT team,

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:15.830
but

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:17.430
maybe,

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:20.550
just maybe, the heightened security

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:23.990
would thwart, as I said the word,

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.990
thwart

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:29.110
the bad guy from wanting to do

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:32.390
something even more so. We know

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:34.698
they got the budget passed today

00:05:34.708 --> 00:05:36.469
in the

00:05:36.479 --> 00:05:40.070
House, and now it's off to the

00:05:40.080 --> 00:05:41.749
president's desk.

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:46.550
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:49.189
Another thing that

00:05:49.199 --> 00:05:52.310
happened—I'm

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:53.990
not trying to attack the 50-year

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.310
mark. I wasn't attacking President Trump.

00:05:56.320 --> 00:05:58.310
I'm

00:05:58.320 --> 00:05:59.670
for President Trump. I pray for him probably more

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:01.590
than I've prayed for any president ever

00:06:01.600 --> 00:06:04.230
before in my life. I have interceded for

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:07.430
this man

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:13.909
because I know what he has to get done

00:06:13.909 --> 00:06:13.919
and

00:06:13.919 --> 00:06:17.189
what the Lord has shown me about

00:06:17.199 --> 00:06:19.749
his future and what he has

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:22.070
to accomplish concerning the end times

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:24.469
and the church. Could God use somebody

00:06:24.479 --> 00:06:26.629
else? Yes, but he has somebody

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:29.590
that he can use right now.

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:33.350
Regarding

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:36.150
the 50-year mortgage, as much as my

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:38.469
opinion is—after I saw how much the

00:06:38.479 --> 00:06:40.230
interest was—people say, 'Braden, it's

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:41.670
affordable and it makes it where I can

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:44.230
buy a house.'If that's your avenue and

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:47.350
this happens, this is what I saw:

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:50.710
a housing boom coming, a mortgage

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:54.950
boom,

00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:58.309
a green arrow going up, and the houses

00:06:58.319 --> 00:07:00.550
were transparent.

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:08.870
I

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:10.230
believe it could be because of the

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:11.510
timing.

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:14.070
I saw it

00:07:14.070 --> 00:07:14.080
coming

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.589
around January

00:07:15.599 --> 00:07:17.909
or

00:07:17.919 --> 00:07:19.830
the first of the year.

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:25.350
Here we are at Thanksgiving,

00:07:25.350 --> 00:07:25.360
and

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:27.990
we're talking about it. So for the

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:30.150
people who want a 50-year

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:32.950
mortgage, praise God. It's not

00:07:32.960 --> 00:07:35.909
my business. Look at that

00:07:35.919 --> 00:07:39.150
graph.

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:43.350
If that's what you're

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.710
believing God for, I'm believing that

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:47.029
you'll be debt-free. I'm believing God

00:07:47.039 --> 00:07:48.790
that you'll owe no man anything but to

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:51.670
love him. I believe that the Bible says

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:53.830
that a seed produces after its own

00:07:53.840 --> 00:07:55.670
kind. Whatsoever man soweth, that will

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:58.309
he also reap. I believe that you won't

00:07:58.319 --> 00:08:00.070
have to have a 50-year mortgage, that

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:01.670
you'll be the lender unto many and you

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:03.589
shall not borrow.

00:08:03.599 --> 00:08:05.350
That's just what I believe. But you have

00:08:05.350 --> 00:08:05.360
to let

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:07.430
people

00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:09.589
be where their faith is. If their

00:08:09.599 --> 00:08:11.909
faith is at a 50-year mortgage,

00:08:11.919 --> 00:08:13.589
you can't knock

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:17.510
them.

00:08:19.280 --> 00:08:21.110
Everybody's been dealt a measure of

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:24.150
faith, but how you exercise

00:08:24.150 --> 00:08:24.160
and

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:26.230
grow

00:08:26.230 --> 00:08:26.240
it

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:29.430
is up to you every single day.

00:08:29.430 --> 00:08:29.440
I'm

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:30.869
not knocking anybody

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:33.029
because I've been there.

00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:34.709
But

00:08:34.719 --> 00:08:36.870
looking at 50

00:08:36.880 --> 00:08:38.550
years is a

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:41.350
long time. I don't even

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:42.709
know if I'll be alive; I had to do the

00:08:42.719 --> 00:08:44.070
math.

00:08:44.070 --> 00:08:44.080
Anyway,

00:08:44.080 --> 00:08:50.230
going over the

00:08:50.230 --> 00:08:50.240
vision—was

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:52.230
there

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:53.670
anything else you want to show

00:08:53.680 --> 00:08:57.269
in the news, baby? Oh,

00:08:57.279 --> 00:09:00.550
I want you to see

00:09:00.560 --> 00:09:04.310
this

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:07.990
video my son found. This is General

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:10.790
Flynn. We met General

00:09:10.800 --> 00:09:14.710
Flynn at Clay

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:16.150
Clark's

00:09:16.160 --> 00:09:17.829
event.

00:09:17.839 --> 00:09:20.630
I want to

00:09:20.640 --> 00:09:24.470
show you what he says about what he

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:26.790
believes we're about to see.

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:29.030
I don't believe he watches my

00:09:29.040 --> 00:09:31.190
channel,

00:09:33.040 --> 00:09:36.150
but he is saying

00:09:36.160 --> 00:09:38.150
what the spirit of God is

00:09:38.150 --> 00:09:38.160
saying—what

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:40.710
I'm warning you about—regarding a major

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:43.990
attack against America. And to pray.

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:46.230
This is why we're here. So, I want you

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:49.190
to play this, Braden, a little bit

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:51.030
and let them hear what General Flynn

00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:55.110
said. He's on the inside. He knows. He

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.430
hears the chatter—that's what I'm trying

00:09:57.440 --> 00:09:59.990
to say. So, that was an amazing

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:01.509
interview, by the way. I would encourage

00:10:01.509 --> 00:10:01.519
everybody—I

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:04.389
get into stuff

00:10:04.399 --> 00:10:05.670
like that when Braden finds stuff

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:07.190
because whenever it's going along with

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:10.870
what the Lord has told me, I go, 'You

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:13.350
know, you don't want to be

00:10:13.350 --> 00:10:13.360
flaky.'There's

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:15.750
so much of what the Lord shows

00:10:15.760 --> 00:10:18.949
me on a consecutive basis that when

00:10:18.959 --> 00:10:20.470
Braden finds me stuff like that, he

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:22.870
goes, 'Daddy, this will encourage you

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:24.790
that what the Lord is telling

00:10:24.800 --> 00:10:26.710
you and what you're praying about all

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:29.110
the time in the car driving around and

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.790
praying in the house when I hear you

00:10:30.790 --> 00:10:30.800
praying—Daddy,

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:32.949
other people are

00:10:32.959 --> 00:10:34.870
saying this, and they're not in your prayer

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:37.190
chain. These are people that are in the

00:10:37.190 --> 00:10:37.200
world.'And

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:39.190
I don't know if General

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:41.430
Flynn knows Jesus Christ or not. I pray

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:43.990
he does. But it's interesting when a man

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:47.190
of his caliber goes on Alex Jones and

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:51.350
warns the nation that he believes in 90

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:54.949
days. Was it 90 days?

00:10:54.959 --> 00:10:58.470
No, he said 40 days. 39 days.

00:10:58.480 --> 00:10:59.590
90. It was 90.

00:10:59.600 --> 00:10:59.910
Okay.

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:00.790
Within 90 days.

00:11:00.800 --> 00:11:02.470
Within 90 days

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:04.550
was the same time frame the Lord said,

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:08.230
all the way going into the 4th of July.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:10.949
Praying into this time frame as I was

00:11:10.959 --> 00:11:12.550
seeing, and people said, 'Brendon, did

00:11:12.560 --> 00:11:17.910
you say many 9/11s?'I said, 'Many

00:11:17.920 --> 00:11:19.910
with a

00:11:19.910 --> 00:11:19.920
Y.'No,

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:22.790
small but many of them.

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:27.430
They're small but many is what I saw.

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:31.910
Like a bunch, but many, like small.

00:11:31.920 --> 00:11:32.870
Does that make sense?

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:33.910
Many, many,

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:36.870
many. It was a play on words, I

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:40.949
guess. But many, many 9/11s.

00:11:40.959 --> 00:11:45.350
This is where I saw a thousand men that

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:49.190
were operatives from a country,

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:53.590
not terrorists, an actual group of men

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:57.350
that were trained people that were here

00:11:57.360 --> 00:11:58.790
and infiltrated. And that's why I tried

00:11:58.790 --> 00:11:58.800
to—a

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:01.190
thousand of them. And I've said it:

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:03.110
10 cities.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:06.310
10 cities over and over again. 100 men

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:08.949
per city

00:12:08.959 --> 00:12:12.470
spread out into towns.

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:15.509
Two men per town. Some of those towns

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:18.949
were bigger; they had three.

00:12:18.959 --> 00:12:21.030
And they spread the people out. And the

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:24.710
Lord said they even, as a flex, went

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:29.110
into Honolulu with three men.

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:32.550
And I saw three men specifically. And

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:33.590
you know what? I thought it was

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:35.190
interesting because, you know, we are

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:38.310
researchers. I always say

00:12:38.310 --> 00:12:38.320
'we'—I

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:41.750
don't pull my toe—and it's Braden

00:12:41.760 --> 00:12:46.629
and Diana who are researchers, and I

00:12:46.639 --> 00:12:49.030
depend on them for so much. And

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:53.269
they said—who was it, you or Braden?—they said,

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:58.230
'I found the 41st

00:12:58.230 --> 00:12:58.240
floor.'Who

00:12:58.240 --> 00:13:01.430
lives on the 41st floor? There's

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:02.949
mama

